{"tid":1135060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳美國伺服器廠商 SuperMicro 放棄中國製零件，轉台製！","createTime":"2019-05-02T05:26:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T02:09:03.000Z","uid":1886,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0f80b82a7aad31266b7eb9af06f583da353bcb67","tid":1135060,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T05:26:59.000Z","msg":"傳美伺服器廠商棄華製零件　擬在台投資100億新台幣<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190430/mobile/bkn-20190430225832282-0430_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190430%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190430225832282-0430_00952_001.html&d=5W7Dp6DGRi9eT2AMHrnJu9Rt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=0e5c865c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190430/mobile/bkn-20190430225832282-0430_00952_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n有美國傳媒報道，該國伺服器製造商美超微電腦（Supermicro Computer）因其當地客戶對網絡間諜風險感憂慮，據悉已指示相關零件供應商，將生產線搬出中國；又稱該企正評估在台灣進一步投資100億元新台幣（約25億港元）。 <br />\n<br />\n報道稱，美超微電腦在華生產的主機板，被植入惡意晶片，該批晶片會攻擊蘋果公司和亞馬遜等大型科技客戶。據悉美超微電腦強烈否認指控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，惟有日媒引述該公司主管，表示公司的美國客戶已要求停止供應在中國生產的電腦主機板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。 <br />\n<br />\n報道又指，除要求供應商遷移生產線，美超微電腦為降低風險，也正在擴建自家製造設施；又稱美超微電腦伺服器系統多由該公司組裝，惟把主機板生產外判給其他供應商；該主管認為，「我們必須提高自我依賴，而不僅依賴這些外判夥伴，過去這些夥伴生產線多數位於中國。」 <br />\n<br />\n報道更提到，該公司斥資20億元新台幣（約5億港元）在桃園興建的新工廠，已於周一（29日）動土，另該企也正在加州矽谷拓展事業版圖。"},{"pid":"e01dbb0ec5850221f66f67a8b0270dc1f6c023a2","tid":1135060,"uid":81113,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T05:52:24.000Z","msg":"中國或成最大然家"},{"pid":"f7117b80b24f69f60ce5afa4978d8a7006ac240f","tid":1135060,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e01dbb0ec5850221f66f67a8b0270dc1f6c023a2","tid":1135060,"uid":81113,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T05:52:24.000Z","msg":"中國或成最大然家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T05:53:14.000Z","msg":"呀，唔係，贏家"},{"pid":"cf5c98fb180e9d2493dfc576ce5033374716b571","tid":1135060,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T05:53:15.000Z","msg":"其實台灣都幾危<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc06a730af7125f3e406dd80131e5aa7255f344","tid":1135060,"uid":48582,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:03:16.000Z","msg":"百份報用字唔當台灣係中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3660f4c8f379b294e279fe879eb5e6c5901167eb","tid":1135060,"uid":15283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:41:04.000Z","msg":"超微好撚大間公司喎，唔知啲中國玻璃心點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82a7b7e692db75cf01ec5d5848741c19fe37d13f","tid":1135060,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:48:46.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"976e68318adbeca18e6b73a3ae485b47bcd22ce7","tid":1135060,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:51:33.000Z","msg":"出賣完d客扮有做嘢"},{"pid":"156cf62b51f74bda2ed92df96228b22b30dca5a5","tid":1135060,"uid":109102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:25:49.000Z","msg":"間嘢個老闆都係台灣人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16cdeed9cd857b67177c749705270957e6958566","tid":1135060,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T01:27:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: purple;\"></span>"},{"pid":"7f80e421dd30c03cc3d3e14dd320af4f9e97744c","tid":1135060,"uid":75193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T02:09:03.000Z","msg":"之前又話有中国間諜野fake news <br />\n而家又轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}